Package ua.java.conferences.controller.actions.implementation.base

This is base package. It contains all base actions implementations. They can be called by any user ChangePasswordAction - to change users password DefaultAction - for any mistake in action's name. Will return index page EditProfileAction - to edit users profile ErrorAction - for any errors ResetPasswordAction - to reset users password SignInAction - to log in to web app SignInAction - to log out from web app SignUpAction - to sign up
